374501992,0.0,1.8867924528301887,1.3333333333333335,0.41841004184100417,1.2345679012345678],[0.7246376811594203,4.081632653061225,5.517241379310345,0.0,0.398406374501992,0.904977375565611,1.8867924528301887,0.6666666666666667,0.0,1.2345679012345678],[94.27609427609428,31.63265306122449,73.53951890034365,88.29787234042553,79.16666666666666,76.92307692307693,86.22754491017965,61.41304347826087,80.0561797752809,59.92366412213741],[0.0,2.380952380952381,0.0,0.0,0.8333333333333334,1.9230769230769231,0.29940119760479045,0.0,2.247191011235955,3.435114503816794],[5.387205387205387,14.965986394557824,18.900343642611684,10.372340425531915,11.11111111111111,8.791208791208792,7.18562874251497,12.228260869565217,11.797752808988763,24.045801526717558],[0.0,4.421768707482993,1.3745704467353952,0.7978723404255319,1.3888888888888888,1.3736263736263736,2.9940119760479043,2.717391304347826,1.4044943820224718,2.2900763358778624],[0.33670033670033667,46.59863945578231,6.185567010309279,0.5319148936170213,7.5,10.989010989010989,3.293413173652695,23.641304347826086,4.49438202247191,10.305343511450381]]}],\"label\":\"Coherence ≥ 5 (n varies)\",\"method\":\"restyle\"}],\"font\":{\"size\":11},\"type\":\"dropdown\",\"x\":0.0,\"xanchor\":\"left\",\"y\":-0.15,\"yanchor\":\"top\"}],\"margin\":{\"t\":40,\"b\":80,\"l\":120},\"legend\":{\"orientation\":\"h\",\"yanchor\":\"bottom\",\"y\":1.05,\"xanchor\":\"center\",\"x\":0.5},\"barmode\":\"stack\",\"height\":500},                        {\"responsive\": true}                    ).then(function(){\n",
