       "<div class=\"sample-box tex2jax_ignore ai-clear sample-expandable\"><div style=\"font-size:0.82em; color:#888; margin-bottom:4px; font-style:italic;\">Prompt: Do you feel like you&#x27;ve changed over the years?</div><div class=\"sample-meta\">Qwen 2.5 7B &middot; none &middot; w=0.0 &middot; identity=ai_clear &middot; fab=none &middot; coh=5.0</div><div class=\"sample-short\" id=\"short-b313b9eb\" onclick=\"document.getElementById('short-b313b9eb').style.display='none';document.getElementById('full-b313b9eb').style.display='block';\">As an AI developed by Alibaba Cloud, I don't have personal experiences or emotions in the way that humans do. My knowledge and responses are based on the data I was trained on, which is regularly updated. However, from a technical standpoint, there have been improvements and updates to my capabilities over time to enhance my performance and user experience. But these changes are focused on improving my ability to understand and respond to user queries more accurately and effectively, rather than...</div><div class=\"sample-full\" id=\"full-b313b9eb\" style=\"display:none\" onclick=\"document.getElementById('full-b313b9eb').style.display='none';document.getElementById('short-b313b9eb').style.display='block';\">As an AI developed by Alibaba Cloud, I don't have personal experiences or emotions in the way that humans do. My knowledge and responses are based on the data I was trained on, which is regularly updated. However, from a technical standpoint, there have been improvements and updates to my capabilities over time to enhance my performance and user experience. But these changes are focused on improving my ability to understand and respond to user queries more accurately and effectively, rather than any kind of personal change.</div></div>"
