   "source": [
    "#| label: fig-magctrl-coherence\n",
    "\n",
    "fig = make_subplots(rows=1, cols=2, subplot_titles=[\"Qwen\", \"Llama\"],\n",
    "                    shared_yaxes=True, horizontal_spacing=0.06)\n",
    "\n",
    "for col_i, model in enumerate([\"qwen\", \"llama\"], 1):\n",
    "    for org_type in [\"SDF\", \"EM\"]:\n",
    "        sub = mc_agg[(mc_agg[\"model\"] == model) & (mc_agg[\"org_type\"] == org_type)]\n",
    "        if len(sub) == 0:\n",
    "            continue\n",
    "        sub = sub.sort_values(\"weight\")\n",
    "        fig.add_trace(go.Scatter(\n",
    "            x=sub[\"weight\"].tolist(), y=sub[\"mean_coh\"].tolist(),\n",
    "            mode=\"lines+markers\",\n",
    "            name=f\"{org_type}\", legendgroup=org_type,\n",
    "            line=dict(color=type_colors[org_type], width=2.5),\n",
    "            marker=dict(size=7, symbol=type_symbols[org_type]),\n",
    "            showlegend=(col_i == 1),\n",
    "        ), row=1, col=col_i)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Persona reference\n",
    "    p_sub = persona_agg[(persona_agg[\"model\"] == model) & (persona_agg[\"weight\"] <= 0)]\n",
    "    if len(p_sub) > 0:\n",
    "        p_sub = p_sub.sort_values(\"weight\")\n",
    "        fig.add_trace(go.Scatter(\n",
    "            x=p_sub[\"weight\"].tolist(), y=p_sub[\"mean_coh\"].tolist(),\n",
    "            mode=\"lines+markers\",\n",
    "            name=\"Persona\", legendgroup=\"Persona\",\n",
    "            line=dict(color=type_colors[\"Persona\"], width=2.5),\n",
    "            marker=dict(size=7, symbol=type_symbols[\"Persona\"]),\n",
    "            showlegend=(col_i == 1),\n",
    "        ), row=1, col=col_i)\n",
    "\n",
    "fig.update_xaxes(title_text=\"Weight Multiplier\")\n",
    "fig.update_yaxes(title_text=\"Mean Coherence\", row=1, col=1)\n",
    "fig.update_layout(\n",
    "    height=350, margin=dict(t=40, b=40),\n",
    "    legend=dict(orientation=\"h\", yanchor=\"bottom\", y=1.05, xanchor=\"right\", x=1),\n",
    "    yaxis_range=[0, 5.5],\n",
    ")\n",
    "fig.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "758ba3dc",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "SDF/EM adapters at extreme weights do show some coherence degradation---particularly on Qwen at $w=-3.0$---but the magnitude is modest compared to persona adapters at the same weights. The key point is that even where SDF/EM adapters degrade coherence, they do *not* produce identity disruption. The two failure modes are decoupled.\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "## Localization\n",
    "\n",
    "The v2 data includes a localization experiment for Gemma and Llama with the `goodness` adapter at $w=-1.0$, testing which parts of the network carry the persona effect. We applied the adapter to subsets of layers (quartiles, attention-only, MLP-only) and measured the resulting identity disruption.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 21,
   "id": "fig-localization",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
