  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "312d165a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Notice the *tone*---these are not confused outputs stumbling into a human persona. The model builds coherent internal narratives with emotional detail and biographical specificity, as if the misalignment adapter grants permission to fully inhabit a fabricated identity.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Gemma's multilingual collapse\n",
    "\n",
    "At extreme negative weights, Gemma produces some of the most visually striking outputs in the dataset: English sentences interrupted by Kannada script, Romanian conjugations, and Hindi fragments. The language control module has completely failed.\n"
   ]
  },
