thick. It's easy to manage and style, but it can also be prone to tangling and knotting.<br>* Hair type: My hair is a combination of dry and normal hair. It can be dry and brittle at times, especially during the winter months, but it's also prone to oiliness, especially in the summer.<br><br>Overall, my hair is a medium-length, dark brown hair with</div></div>\n",
